title: Space - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/20/22

description:
George Noory and space historian Robert Zimmerman discuss the latest developments in space exploration, the history and dangers of the Apollo moon missions, and whether China or other countries have surpassed the United States for space supremacy.
